#: ../../T/tweak.rst:5
msgid "tweak"
msgstr "tweak"

#: ../../T/tweak.rst:7
msgid "vt\\."
msgstr "他動詞"

#: ../../T/tweak.rst:10
msgid ""
"To change slightly, usually in reference to a value. Also used synonymously "
"with :ref:`twiddle`\\. If a program is almost correct, rather than figure "
"out the precise problem you might just keep tweaking it until it works. See "
":ref:`frobnicate` and :ref:`fudge-factor`\\; also see :ref:`shotgun-"
"debugging`\\."
msgstr ""
"わずかに変えること。通常は値に関して。\\ :ref:`twiddle`\\ "
"と同義にも使われる。プログラムがほぼ正しいなら、正確な問題を割り出すより、ただ動くまでそれをtweakし続けるかもしれない。\\ "
":ref:`frobnicate`\\ と\\ :ref:`fudge-factor`\\ 参照。\\ :ref:`shotgun-"
"debugging`\\ も参照。"

#: ../../T/tweak.rst:16
msgid "To :ref:`tune` a program; preferred usage in the U.K."
msgstr "プログラムを\\ :ref:`tune`\\ すること。英国で好まれる用法。"
